  "instruction": "On the Demoblaze storefront, open Monitors, open Apple monitor 24, add it to the cart, open the cart, and stop by asking for confirmation before clicking Place Order.",
  "url": "https://demoblaze.com/",
  "source": {
    "site_id": "demoblaze",
